OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fsees more rain and cloud with some
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Continuing into Monday
OL,8,Fwith heavy rain, possible
OL,9,Fthunderstorms. Staying unsettled
OL,10,Fthrough the week as temperatures
OL,11,Freturn to average.
